title: The Collected Mouse Guard (2007->) (Digital) (Empire)
description:
Contains:

FALL 1152 - The first six-issue series, published in 2006-2007. Original Digital-TPB Hi-Res release from Empire.

WINTER 1152 - The second six-issue series, published in 2007-2009. Original Digital-TPB Hi-Res release from Empire.

THE BLACK AXE - The third six-issue series, published in 2010-2013. Pseudo-TPB compiled from the single-issue Digital Hi-Res re-releases from Empire.

LEGENDS OF THE GUARD, VOLUME ONE - The first four-issue anthology series, written and illustrated by guest artists, published in 2010. Original Digital-TPB Mid-Res release from Cypher-Empire.

LEGENDS OF THE GUARD, VOLUME TWO - The second four-issue anthology series, published in 2013. Pseudo-TPB compiled from the single-issue Digital Hi-Res original releases from Empire.

SHORTS - Four shorter (8 to 12 pages) stories, from the publisher's 2010-2013 FCBD anthology issues. All Minutemen releases, Mixed-Res.

Misses:

Nothing whatsoever, as far as I am aware. Woot!
